snippet.title: Jiangshi x Daoshi Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Prepare to be blown away! Jiangshi x Daoshi is an epic story of Chinese vampires, dao priests, assassins and immortals, told in a spectacularly animated visual novel format.

Episode 1+2 now available for free on PC!
itch.io - https://fruitbat-factory.itch.io/daoshi
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1338460/Jiangshi_x_Daoshi/
https://fruitbat-factory.itch.io/daoshi
